A ranar Lahadi, wani dutse ya faɗa a kan Congo Canyon, wanda hakan ya janyo karyewar wasu wayoyin kebir na ƙarƙashin teku a West African Cable System (WASC) da kuma South Atlantic 3 (SAT-3)--ta Afirka ta Kudu .
Domin ƙarin bayani, an yanke SAT-3 ranar Lahadi da safe, yayain da WASC ta faɗi da yamma.
An sanya su a Atlantin Ocean, wanda yake haɗa Afirka ta Kudu da sauran ƙasashen Afirka zuwa Turao.
Karyewar ta faru ne tsakanin Democratic Republic of Congo da kuma Cameroon ta amfani da Coherant Optical Time Domain Reflectometer da tsarin ya samar domin auna nisa.
Wannan karyewar ta nuna abu ɗaya: rashin ƙarfin yanar gizo.
