Alal misali, Openserve sun ce karyewar ta shafi masu amfani da private leased circuit services na duniya a hanyar sadarwarsu.
Kuma sun ce sanya hannun jarinsu a ƙarin wasu hanyoyin zai ba wa abokan hulɗa damar cigaba da amfana da sadarwar interdnet wacce babu gargada.
