Wannan labarin ya zo ne kwana biyu bayan jami’an tsaron kenya sun dakatar da aikin Worldcoin a kasar saboda matsalar data.
Sun ce ayyukan kamfanin zai kasance a dakace har sai sanda manyan hukumomi sun tabbatar da cewa ba ta da wata matsala ga mutanen Kenya.
Aikin wanda Sam Altman ya samar, ɗaya daga cikin wanda suke samar da OpenAl (ChatGPT), an ƙaddamar da shi don ƙera mahallin bayanai na harkar kuɗi na duniya ga kowa a duniya.
Aikin yana amfani da wata na’ura mai suna orb domin ɗaukar hoton idon mutane sannan kuma a basu ID na duniya, wanda aka sani da “proof of personhood.”
Wannan ID din na duniya yana taimakawa mutane su tantance shaidarsu ta manhajojin yanar gizoba tare da bayyana sunayensu ko wasu bayanan sun a sirri ba.
Yayin da aka yi wa Worldcoin rijista a matsayin masu kula da bayanai a Kenya, mahukunta sun ce bashi da doka.
