A farko an yi zaton samun asarar miliyan $49.2, Uber sun ɓige da zaton da samun ribar miliyan $394.
Ɗaya daga cikin dalilan da suka bada gudunmawar samun ribar shi ne ƙarin 22% a tafiye-tafiye na manhajar da kuma tarbiyyar kuɗi.
