Kamfanin Flex Finance bashi kaɗai ne sabon kamfani dake hango damammaki a wajen tallafawa ƴan kasuwar Afrika su tsara hanyar kashe kuɗaɗensu ba.
Sava — wani sabon kamfani ne dake Afrika ta Kudu daya tara dala miliyan $2 a shekarar 2022—, da Bujati, wani kamfani da YC ke marawa baya, sune abokan gasar Flex na kai tsaye.
