Wani sabon rahoto kan satar ta banki da Cibiyar Horarwa ta Kuɗi (FITC) ta fitar ta bayyana cewa 'yan Najeriya sunyi asarar 85.1% ƙasa da kuɗin da ake sata ta banki a farkon rubu'in 2023 idan aka kwatanta da Q4 na 2022.
A Q1 na 2023, 'yan Najeriya sunyi asarar Naira miliyan ₦472 daga jimillar ƙararraki 12,533 da aka ruwaito.
A kwatance, sunyi asarar Naira biliyan ₦3.1 a cikin ƙararraki 14,609 a Q4 na 2022.
Bisa wannan rahoto, bankuna sun dawo da kaso 85.13 cikin ɗari wanda kuɗaɗe ne masu yawa fiye da rubu'in baya da kuma ƙarancin ƙararraki da aka ruwaito - ƙasa da 14.07%.
